<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="&quot;IMAGE_2&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORI_IMG"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The black and white image captures a dynamic and intense close-up of two elk engaged in a head-to-head confrontation, likely sparring or fighting. Both elk are depicted from the head and shoulder up, with their large, multi-tined antlers prominently interlocked. The elk on the left is shown in profile, with its head lowered and facing right, its dark body partially visible. Its antlers are expansive and complex, with several points branching upwards and forwards. The elk on the right is seen more from a three-quarter view, also with its head lowered and angled towards the left, its eyes appearing focused on the struggle. Its antlers are equally impressive, intricately woven with those of the other elk, forming a powerful central point of conflict. The fur of both animals appears dark due to the grayscale nature of the image, suggesting a deep brown or black color. The background is softly blurred and out of focus, hinting at a natural outdoor environment, possibly a grassy or rocky terrain, which emphasizes the elk as the sole subjects of the image. The overall atmosphere conveyed is one of raw power, natural struggle, and intense concentration."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_2.jpg</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LEFT ELK&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A large, dark-colored male elk, positioned on the left side of the image. Its head is lowered, and its prominent, branched antlers are interlocked with those of the other elk, indicating a physical confrontation or sparring."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_2.jpg</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;RIGHT ELK&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A large, dark-colored male elk, positioned on the right side of the image. Its head is lowered, and its prominent, branched antlers are interlocked with those of the other elk, indicating a physical confrontation or sparring."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_2.jpg</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LEFT ELK'S ANTLERS&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The large, complex, branched antlers belonging to the elk on the left. They are dark and appear sturdy, currently engaged and interlocked with the antlers of the right elk."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_2.jpg</data>
</node>
